data.description: Welcome to this lovely starter home with an amazing 3 car garage nestled in a serene and peaceful neighborhood. This property offers the perfect blend of character and functionality, featuring original hardwood floors, two bedrooms on the main level, a partially finished basement with an additional bedroom, and a host of updates that make it a fantastic opportunity for a discerning buyer.Main Level Highlights:- As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the warm and inviting living room, complete with original hardwood floors that are ready to be brought back to their former glory with some refinishing.- The spacious living room also boasts a convenient coat closet, ensuring you have ample storage for your outerwear.- Adjacent to the living room is a separate dining room, perfect for hosting gatherings and enjoying meals with family and friends.- The kitchen has been tastefully updated with new flooring and painted cabinets, providing a fresh and modern feel to the heart of the home.- Two generously sized bedrooms on this level offer comfortable spaces for rest and relaxation.- The full bathroom on the main level features an updated tub, combining style and functionality for your daily routines.Basement Features:- Descend to the partially finished basement, where you'll find an additional bedroom, a bonus room or 4th bedroom, and a convenient half bath, offering versatility and potential for various uses.  - In the basement, there is also a workshop area, ideal for DIY projects, crafts, or hobbies.- The laundry area is conveniently located in the basement, providing practicality and ease for your laundry needs. Exterior and Garage:- The exterior of the house boasts new gutters on the house as well as new shingles on both the house and the garage, ensuring long-lasting protection and curb appeal.- Step outside to discover a vinyl fenced backyard, offering privacy and a safe play area for pets or children.- The true standout of this property is the oversized 26 x 38 triple garage with a 26 x 24 loft. This remarkable space is a dream for hobbyists, DIY enthusiasts, or anyone in need of substantial storage or workspace.- The garage is equipped with 220 wiring circuit and outlets for a welder and air compressor, making it a haven for those with mechanical or crafting interests.- Access the garage with ease through a man door or from a 16' x 7' overhead door, complete with a Chamberlain opener, as well as a second 9' x 11' overhead door.Additional Details:- Located in a quiet neighborhood, you'll enjoy a peaceful and tranquil setting while having easy access to schools, parks, and essential amenities.- A new water heater was installed in the last year, ensuring reliable and efficient hot water for your daily needs.- Ductwork is in place for a central air conditioning unit to be installed, offering the potential for year-round comfort.This property is a true gem, offering a delightful blend of vintage charm and modern convenience. Don't miss your chance to make this your own and take full advantage of the impressive garage space that will surely appeal to those seeking the perfect space for their hobbies and interests. Schedule a showing today to explore all the possibilities this wonderful home has to offer!
